---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const lastUpdated = "December 22, 2025";
---

<BaseLayout
    title="Privacy Policy | Queens Auto Service"
    description="Privacy Policy for Queens Auto Service in Elgin, IL. Learn how we collect, use, and safeguard your personal data."
>
    <section class="py-20 lg:py-28 bg-white dark:bg-transparent">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">
            <h1
                class="display-hero-page text-queens-primary dark:text-white mb-6"
            >
                Privacy Policy
            </h1>
            <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-12 text-lg">
                Last Revised: {lastUpdated}
            </p>

            <div
                class="prose prose-lg prose-blue max-w-none text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 dark:prose-invert"
            >
                <div>
                    <p><strong>Effective Date: {lastUpdated}</strong></p>
                </div>

                <h2
                    class="text-2xl font-bold text-queens-primary dark:text-white mt-12 mb-6"
                >
                    Who We Are
                </h2>
                <p>
                    Our website address is: <a
                        href="https://queensautoserviceselgin.com"
                        class="text-queens-primary dark:text-blue-400 underline"
                        >https://queensautoserviceselgin.com</a
                    >. Queens Auto is a full-service auto repair shop based in
                    Elgin, IL. This privacy policy outlines how we collect, use,
                    and safeguard your personal data.
                </p>

                <h2
                    class="text-2xl font-bold text-queens-primary dark:text-white mt-12 mb-6"
                >
                    What Personal Data We Collect and Why We Collect It
                </h2>

                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Comments</h3>
                <p>
                    When visitors leave comments on the site, we collect the
                    data shown in the comments form, along with the visitor’s IP
                    address and browser user agent string to assist with spam
                    detection.
                </p>
                <p>
                    An anonymized string created from your email address (a
                    hash) may be provided to the Gravatar service to check for
                    use. Gravatar’s privacy policy is available at Gravatar
                    Privacy Policy. Once your comment is approved, your profile
                    picture becomes visible publicly next to your comment.
                </p>

                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Media</h3>
                <p>
                    If you upload images to the website, you should avoid
                    uploading images with embedded location data (EXIF GPS)
                    included. Visitors can download and extract location data
                    from such images.
                </p>

                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">SMS Communication</h3>
                <p>
                    By providing your phone number and opting in, you consent to
                    receive SMS messages from Queens Auto for purposes such as
                    appointment reminders, service updates, and limited-time
                    offers. Message frequency may vary.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Standard message and data rates may apply. You can opt out
                    at any time by replying STOP, and receive assistance by
                    replying HELP or contacting us directly at <a
                        href="mailto:contact@queensautoserviceselgin.com"
                        class="text-queens-primary dark:text-blue-400 underline"
                        >contact@queensautoserviceselgin.com</a
                    >.
                </p>
                <p>
                    We do not share, rent, or sell your phone number to third
                    parties. Your information is stored securely and used only
                    for the purposes outlined above.
                </p>
                <p>Consent is not a condition of purchase.</p>
                <p>
                    Carriers are not liable for delayed or undelivered messages.
                </p>

                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Contact Forms</h3>
                <p>
                    When you fill out a contact form, we collect your name,
                    email address, phone number, and any additional information
                    you choose to provide. This information is used strictly to
                    respond to your inquiry or provide services requested. We do
                    not use this information for unsolicited marketing.
                </p>

                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Cookies</h3>
                <p>
                    If you leave a comment on our site, you may opt-in to saving
                    your name, email, and website in cookies. These are for your
                    convenience, so you don’t have to re-enter your details when
                    leaving another comment. These cookies last one year.
                </p>
                <p>
                    If you visit our login page, we set a temporary cookie to
                    check if your browser accepts cookies. This cookie contains
                    no personal data and is discarded when you close your
                    browser.
                </p>
                <p>
                    When you log in, we set up cookies to save your login
                    details and screen preferences. Login cookies last two days,
                    and screen option cookies last one year. Selecting “Remember
                    Me” extends login cookies to two weeks. Logging out removes
                    login cookies.
                </p>
                <p>
                    If you edit or publish an article, a cookie with the post ID
                    will be saved in your browser. This expires after one day.
                </p>

                <h2
                    class="text-2xl font-bold text-queens-primary dark:text-white mt-12 mb-6"
                >
                    Embedded Content from Other Websites
                </h2>
                <p>
                    Articles may include embedded content (e.g., videos, images,
                    articles). Embedded content from other websites behaves as
                    if you visited that website directly. These sites may
                    collect your data, use cookies, embed third-party tracking,
                    and monitor your interaction with their content.
                </p>

                <h2
                    class="text-2xl font-bold text-queens-primary dark:text-white mt-12 mb-6"
                >
                    Analytics
                </h2>
                <p>
                    We use Google Analytics and similar tools to understand how
                    visitors interact with our website. These services may
                    collect IP addresses, device information, browser types, and
                    pages visited. This data helps us improve user experience
                    and website performance.
                </p>

                <h2
                    class="text-2xl font-bold text-queens-primary dark:text-white mt-12 mb-6"
                >
                    Who We Share Your Data With
                </h2>
                <p>
                    We do not sell or rent your personal information. Data may
                    be shared with trusted third-party service providers who
                    assist with operations such as hosting, analytics, SMS
                    delivery, and email communication — only to the extent
                    necessary for service delivery and under strict
                    confidentiality agreements.
                </p>

                <h2
                    class="text-2xl font-bold text-queens-primary dark:text-white mt-12 mb-6"
                >
                    How Long We Retain Your Data
                </h2>
                <p>
                    If you leave a comment, the comment and its metadata are
                    retained indefinitely. For registered users (if any), we
                    store personal information in user profiles, which users can
                    access, edit, or delete at any time (except usernames).
                    Admins may also access and manage this data.
                </p>

                <h2
                    class="text-2xl font-bold text-queens-primary dark:text-white mt-12 mb-6"
                >
                    What Rights You Have Over Your Data
                </h2>
                <p>
                    If you have an account or have left comments, you can
                    request an exported file of the personal data we hold about
                    you. You can also request deletion of your personal data,
                    except where we are required to retain it for legal,
                    administrative, or security purposes.
                </p>

                <h2
                    class="text-2xl font-bold text-queens-primary dark:text-white mt-12 mb-6"
                >
                    Where We Send Your Data
                </h2>
                <p>
                    Visitor comments may be checked through an automated spam
                    detection service.
                </p>

                <h2
                    class="text-2xl font-bold text-queens-primary dark:text-white mt-12 mb-6"
                >
                    Your Contact Information
                </h2>
                <p>
                    To request access, updates, or deletion of your personal
                    data, contact us at:
                </p>
                <p>
                    <strong>Queens Auto Service</strong><br />
                    1303 Dundee Ave<br />
                    Elgin, IL 60120<br />
                    Email: <a
                        href="mailto:contact@queensautoserviceselgin.com"
                        class="text-queens-primary dark:text-blue-400 underline"
                        >contact@queensautoserviceselgin.com</a
                    ><br />
                    Phone: <a
                        href="tel:2243653000"
                        class="text-queens-primary dark:text-blue-400 underline"
                        >(224) 365-3000</a
                    >
                </p>

                <h2
                    class="text-2xl font-bold text-queens-primary dark:text-white mt-12 mb-6"
                >
                    Additional Information
                </h2>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">
                    How We Protect Your Data
                </h3>
                <p>
                    We implement technical and organizational security measures
                    including secure servers, encrypted connections (HTTPS),
                    firewall protection, access controls, and employee training
                    to safeguard your information.
                </p>

                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">
                    What Data Breach Procedures We Have in Place
                </h3>
                <p>
                    In the event of a data breach, we will notify affected
                    individuals and relevant authorities as required by law, and
                    take immediate steps to contain and remedy the breach.
                </p>

                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">
                    What Third Parties We Receive Data From
                </h3>
                <p>
                    We may receive limited data from third-party platforms such
                    as scheduling tools or payment processors strictly for
                    operational purposes.
                </p>

                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">
                    What Automated Decision Making and/or Profiling We Do With
                    User Data
                </h3>
                <p>
                    We do not use automated decision-making or profiling based
                    on your data.
                </p>

                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">
                    Industry Regulatory Disclosure Requirements
                </h3>
                <p>
                    We comply with all applicable consumer protection, privacy,
                    and data security regulations under U.S. and Illinois law.
                </p>

                <p
                    class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 italic"
                >
                    If you have any questions or concerns about this policy,
                    please contact us.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</BaseLayout>
